<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sindika Integrated E-Warta - Warta Digital Terintegrasi</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        .feature-card {
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-purple-50 to-pink-50 min-h-screen">
         <%- include('partials/_navbar') %>

    <main class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pt-32 pb-16">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-2xl mb-6">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v1m2 13a2 2 0 01-2-2V7m2 13a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2m-4-3H9M7 16h6M7 8h6v4H7V8z" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">E-Warta Digital</h1>
            <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium text-purple-600 mb-6">Modernisasi Warta Gereja Anda</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Ucapkan selamat tinggal pada proses distribusi warta manual. Terintegrasi penuh dengan Sindika Storage API untuk mengunggah, mengarsipkan, dan mendistribusikan warta digital langsung kepada seluruh jemaat.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-12">
            <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7v8a2 2 0 002 2h6M8 7V5a2 2 0 012-2h4.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l4.414 4.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V15a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2M8 7H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2v-2" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Arsip Digital Terpusat</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600">Semua edisi warta tersimpan rapi dan aman. Jemaat dapat mengakses arsip warta edisi sebelumnya kapan pun mereka butuhkan.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 19l9 2-9-18-9 18 9-2zm0 0v-8" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Distribusi Instan</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600">Publikasikan warta dan langsung tersebar ke seluruh jemaat melalui notifikasi push dan akses web. Tidak perlu lagi cetak dan bagikan manual.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Jadwal Ibadah Terintegrasi</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600">Tampilkan jadwal ibadah mingguan, pengumuman penting, dan informasi pelayanan langsung dalam warta digital yang interaktif.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card p-8 bg-white/70 backdrop-blur-lg border border-white/50 rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-600 rounded-xl mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Analytics & Engagement</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600">Pantau berapa banyak jemaat yang membaca warta, fitur mana yang paling sering diakses, dan tingkatkan engagement gereja Anda.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 p-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-pink-600 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl text-white text-center">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Wujudkan Gereja Digital</h3>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-purple-100">Ramah lingkungan, hemat biaya cetak, dan menjangkau jemaat di mana pun mereka berada.</p>
            <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-purple-600 font-semibold rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all">
                Mulai Gunakan E-Warta
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>
     <%- include('partials/_footer') %> 
</body>
</html>